Package: hystar
Title: Simulation and Estimation of the Hysteretic TAR Model
Version: 0.0.9
Date: 2022-11-10
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Daan", "de Jong", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"), 
        email = "d.dejong@uu.nl", 
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6034-0136")
        ),
    person(
        "European Research Council", 
        role = "fnd"
        )
    )
Maintainer: Daan de Jong <d.dejong@uu.nl>
Description: Simulates data from and estimates parameters of the hysteretic
    threshold autoregressive (HysTAR) model. Estimation is implemented using 
    the conditional least squares method. See Li, Guan, Li and Yu (2015) 
    <doi:10.1093/biomet/asv017> for details about the model.
